description.3: Peter's movie night to see Star Trek: The Motion Picture is interrupted by the arrival of...Dazzler! The X-Men's resident Disco Queen is under attack by a mysterious orb of light. Will Spider-Man be able to protect the mutant songstress from this menace? Dazzler, under possession by Lightmaster!
description.4: Falcon decides to take a break from the team. Wonder Man rejoins the team. The Wasp becomes infatuated with a criminally insane man who seeks the Avengers' help. But is the man known only as "Selbe" the person he claims to be?
description.5: More machine than man, it shambles forward slowly, hesitantly, as if unwilling to step from the dark shadows of the lab that gave it life! Enter a monster gone berserk, Adonis!
description.8: Han is unwittingly leading the Rebel fleet into a trap.  Can Luke warn him in time?
description.13: Spider-Man teams up with GHOST RIDER to take down the mysteriously mystic MOONDARK! But first, the Wall-Crawler and the Spirit of Vengeance must survive...the CARNIVAL OF FEAR!
description.14: When the team returns to New York, Nighthawk is arrested by federal agents! Meanwhile, in Tunnelworld, Hulk is captured!
description.15: The Hulk and Daredevil get into a brawl that will leave one of them nearly dead by story's end...
description.16: Is there any hope of Johnny Blaze being cured of his amnesia? Find out!
description.17: Hulk is ambushed at the Gamma Base by Glenn Talbot...who has military orders to kill the Hulk! Will Hulk be slain before he can rescue the body of his love, Jarella?
description.18: To defeat the Hulk, Iron Man must channel all of his power into one single punch!
description.19: The origin of Timothy Braverman, AKA the Gamesman!
description.21: The Futurist terrorizes New York City. But is he smart enough to not be fooled by Blastaar? The force of these two spells peril for the Fantastic Four!
description.22: The Amazing Spider-Man has been transformed into the Spider-Lizard!
description.24: After initial disagreement, Punisher and Spider-Man work together to uncover Lorenzo Jacobi's drug ring. Bugle reporter April Maye enters dangerous territory on an undercover assignment. The Daily Bugle is intent on this scoop- the fall of New York City's worst drug dealer! Will Punisher and Spidey give Jacobi the shakedown he desperately deserves?
description.25: Inferno is wreaking havoc in the life of Tim Turpin, Joe Conroy's co-worker who led to Conroy's death. Will the Avengers step in before Inferno destroys the Liberty Bridge in retaliation?
description.26: The Shield Slinger is targeted when the Adonis, Eric Cameron, returns. With a sinister plan to kill Steve Rogers to gain Life Eternal, Adonis will give the Star-Spangled Soldier the fight of his life!
description.27: Luke is in a lightsaber duel for a life as the Empire attempts to acquire a new deadly weapon.
description.34: Black Panther's investigation uncovers dark secrets -- including a connection between the Dragon Circle and the Ku Klux Klan!
description.37: Johnny Blaze no more! Everything changes when Johnny Blaze loses his memory.
description.38: While in Los Angeles, the Hulk is suddenly attacked! Will the Green Goliath destroy the Living Colossus and finally get some much-deserved downtime?
description.39: Tony agrees to help Bruce Banner get rid of the Hulk.
description.40: Spider-Woman goes into detective mode to uncover the Gamesman's motives and identity.
description.42: Peter Parker throws anonymity to the wind, and instead embraces celebrity! What if Spider-Man chose show business over heroism? But someone's got a death wish for movie star Peter Parker, and Daredevil's keen to solve the mystery!
description.43: The FF are aiding Reed's former colleague Randolph James in a lab invasion, when word is caught that Blastaar is reigning terror upon the Baxter Building!
description.44: Chip Martin isn't leaving the ESU campus without a fight!
description.45: Ben Grimm's got his work cut out for him trying to deal with the IMPOSSIBLE MAN! What silly tricks does the otherworldly imp have in store for Ben this time around? Featuring three of the Fantastic Four's most dastardly foes!
description.48: Wong is gone and Mordo is missing! It's up to Strange and Clea to find them.
description.49: Things look bad for the Defenders with Hellcat and Valkyrie under the power of Mandrill’s mind control, but Nighthawk’s intervention might be enough to set them free! The Hulk, Dr. Strange and the Sub-Mariner continue their adventure in Tunnelworld.
description.50: Han, Luke and Chewie...stranded in the Tatooine desert.  And the Jawas are their only hope.
description.55: Spider-Man and Peter Parker come up against Punisher, and it's far from pretty! Spider-Man busts the Punisher interrogating drug dealers, and is able to dissuade him from lethal force. Peter Parker is covering a story on drug lord Lorenzo Jacobi- the same man Punisher's trying to kill! All trails lead to Spidey, as Punisher draws a connection between Peter and Jacobi!
description.56: With Gyrich relinquishing control over the Avengers, Iron Man considers candidates to fill out their current roster. However, if Wonder Man joins the team, Scarlet Witch will walk. Hawkeye has disconnected his phone, and Hank Pym is having too much fun researching insects.
description.57: Captain America versus the world! There's a new villain in town and his name is the Manipulator! Captain America will have to confront the world to stop this villain. Read, to witness the shocking ending!
description.62: Daredevil follows in his father's boxing footsteps after a case of amnesia wipes his memory clean. But will Murdock see beneath the guise of his corrupt manager? The Man Without Fear becomes a prizefighting champion!
description.63: Reed Richards experiences a major scientific breakthrough with his new energy transmitter device! But Mr. Fantastic's wonderful discovery catches the attention of a particular evil alien race...the Skrulls! And through their normal means of deceit, the Skrulls' prime ten invade the Baxter Building and attack the FF!
description.64: Ghost Rider comes up against a man who has harnessed the power of a nuclear reactor!
description.65: Hulk believes all is well when he defeats Tyrannus and goes off to save Jarella! But Hulk has caused destruction in the golden city of El Dorado, and now the Gamma Base is in hot pursuit!
description.66: During an investigation regarding the deaths of four Stark Enterprises scientists in Hong Kong, Tony is attacked by a dragon.
description.67: Scotty McDowell recruits Spider-Woman to hunt down the notorious Killer Clown.
description.69: Johnny's teammates have fallen from the Skrull's ageing ray! Will Tony Stark prove an ally to the FF?
description.70: A vampire crashes Peter's party! Moribus hunts again.
description.72: Ben Grimm manages to escape a near-death experience, but his FF teammates don’t fare as well. The Stranger arrives, only to find that the Thing and the Hulk are the heroes who can aid him on his strange mission!
description.79: Luke returns to Tatooine for the first time, but his homecoming is cut short by the Empire.
description.81: The Thing is joined by the FF's Human Torch to put out fires around town!
description.83: Doctor Strange, the Hulk, and Sub-Mariner learn about their new angelic companion, Aeroika, in Tunnelworld. Back on Earth, Wasp, Valkyrie and Hellcat have to face the mutant known as Mandrill!
description.84: The Amazing Spider-Man's 200th issue! After surviving an overdose of anti-depressants at the hands of Mysterio, Spider-Man is left powerless. Who is Spider-Man without spider abilities? A mystery surfaces about the true demise of Aunt May, while Peter Parker rues his life as a super hero. Teenage angst never looked, and read, so good! Stan "The Man" Lee joins Marv Wolfman as co-writer in this Anniversary Special!
description.85: The Avengers vs. the Grey Gargoyle! Scarlet Witch transforming stone and flesh with her hex powers! Plus, tantrum-prone Gyrich releases some control over the Avengers, after a lawsuit is awarded in the team's favor.
description.86: In his efforts to stop organized crime in Brooklyn, Captain America comes across his morally grey counterpart, the Punisher. Is Steve Rogers and Frank Castle alike in more ways than one? Find out in "Fear Grows in Brooklyn"!
description.87: Featuring the Black Panther! An assault on T'Challa's life restores his memories of an old unsolved mystery.
description.89: On a clear night in northeastern British Columbia, the incredible Hulk plunges unconscious to the ground! Alerted to the Hulk's presence, a secret unit of the Canadian Ministry of Defense—code-named Department H—sends Dr. Walter Langkowski, AKA Sasquatch, to contain the emerald menace.
description.91: The dawning of the Age of AQUARIAN! Wundarr is back with a new name and improved powers!
description.93: STRANGE RETURNS TO NEW YORK! A night out with Clea goes completely wrong when Strange's neighbor's boyfriend is attacked and killed by a mystical creature that possesses dark magic.
description.94: Doctor Strange summons the Hulk and the Sub-Mariner to his Sanctum Sanctorum for a mission to Tunnel World. In Las Vegas, the team is joined by Yellowjacket as they answer a distress call from a military base.
description.95: Illusions twist and bend into reality, as a still-recovering Spider-Man is victim to Mysterio's torture. Will the end of Spider-Man be a rapidly filling swimming pool? When it comes to Mysterio, all bets are off the table!
description.96: It's never a dull moment for the Avengers, as the team must defeat a primordial ooze-creature that hatched in Brooklyn's Jamaica Bay!
description.97: Even America's Champion can deny the enjoyment of a good old fashion brawl! Captain America finds himself going up against the likes of the Big Thunder and the Coney Island Cruisers! Find out and see who ends up on top!
description.98: Can Leia recruit Metalorn, a factory planet, to turn their back on the Empire?

6.text: Big Ben Donovan and Power Man, kidnapped by the Maggia! But Iron Fist and Thunderbolt are hot on the rescue trail; the duo infiltrates Caesar Cicero's penthouse for information…and track Cage and Donovan to a cemetery!

7.text: Two Machine Men leads to one giant altercation! Maggie's affections for Aaron continue to grow.

9.text: RUN FOR YOUR LIFE! The X-Men have rescued Kitty Pryde. Now it is time to take the fight to the White Queen and recue their comrades. Prepare for a psychic battle between Emma Frost and Phoenix!

10.text: The Savage She-Hulk stops a running bus in its tracks without breaking a sweat!

11.text: A mysterious celestial being called Her is after Adam Warlock, and thinks that Alicia Masters is the key to finding him. Thing must team up with Starhawk in order to save her!

28.text: Elaine and Man-Thing find themselves in more trouble than last issue, this time confronting a primordial race of ‘snowmen’!

29.text: Black Jack Tarr and Shang-Chi face Fu Manchu at last, but one of them may not leave his citadel alive!

34.text: Black Panther's investigation uncovers dark secrets -- including a connection between the Dragon Circle and the Ku Klux Klan!

35.text: DAZZLER Phoenix and Cyclops are on the hunt for a new mutant when they are attacked by a group of Mandroids who are eerily familiar with their power sets. Plus, Kitty Pryde escapes!

36.text: She-Hulk's first appearance and origin issue! Check it out!

46.text: Spider-Man and the Beast join forces against the dastardly duo of Killer Shrike and the Modular Man!

51.text: This is it! Shang-Chi is abducted by his evil father!

58.text: When a wounded Big Ben Donovan crashes into the Gem Theater with blazing guns behind him, Power Man springs into action! And when Man Mountain Marko shows up to rival Power Man, Iron Fist joins the fray!

59.text: Aaron finds the insurance business more hazardous than expected when he faces a personal attack!

60.text: GOD SPARE THE CHILD... Kitty Pryde has been offered scholarships at both the Xavier Institute and Emma Frost's Massachusetts Academy. Where will she go? Plus, the X-Men engage...the Hellfire Club!

61.text: When the X-Men enter Nightcrawler's Inferno, they'll need the help of the Sorceror Supreme Doctor Strange to escape!

68.text: Odin, Zeus, and the Olympians confront Thor in Olympia with designs on razing it into oblivion, even if it means that Thor perishes as well!

72.text: Ben Grimm manages to escape a near-death experience, but his FF teammates don’t fare as well. The Stranger arrives, only to find that the Thing and the Hulk are the heroes who can aid him on his strange mission!

73.text: Man-Thing is accidentally transported to the frozen Himalayas! And a group of expeditioners might need his help!

74.text: Shang Chi and Tarr reach Fu Manchu's headquarters in South America, while Reston and Leiko head to Casablanca.

78.text: An interdimensional adventure starring our cosmically-charged hero- Mar-Vell of the Kree!

80.text: It's Spidey and Doctor Strange vs. Doctor Doom and Dormammu in one epic Annual!

87.text: Featuring the Black Panther! An assault on T'Challa's life restores his memories of an old unsolved mystery.

88.text: Proteus has taken Moira hostage while the X-Men wage their final assault-this time, with designs on taking the evil mutant down for good. Will the combined might of the X-Men be enough to defeat Proteus and save Moira?

Proteus has taken Moira hostage while the X-Men wage their final assault-this time, with designs on taking the evil mutant down for good. Will the combined might of the X-Men be enough to defeat Proteus and save Moira?

89.text: On a clear night in northeastern British Columbia, the incredible Hulk plunges unconscious to the ground! Alerted to the Hulk's presence, a secret unit of the Canadian Ministry of Defense—code-named Department H—sends Dr. Walter Langkowski, AKA Sasquatch, to contain the emerald menace.

99.text: Convinced Alan Cavenaugh is the Big Apple Bomber, the Heroes for Hire release their former friend to the NYPD. But there’s a greater threat lurking in the Halwani embassy! Iron Fist pays a visit to Princess Azir only to be attacked by her guards. Can the Heroes for Hire aid Iron Fist and uncover the Big Apple Bomber’s identity? Or will the city have to endure yet another explosion?
